      "rationale": "In-vitro loop used bovine blood analog (hematocrit 33 ± 1%), temperature 37 ± 0.5 °C, flow rate 3.5 ± 0.05 L/min. CFD boundary conditions set to match measured values. All deviations within ±3%. Criterion met."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
